"{\"uid\": \"sbs.com.au-news-article-paris-olympics-day-three-ocallaghan-defeats-titmus-in-epic-200m-freestyle-showdown-t1sbfico7\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Stream free online, anytime  Discover your world of SBS  Sign in or create an account  or  Stream free online, anytime  Get in touch:  Highlights around SBS:  Follow Us:  SBS acknowledges the Traditional Custodians of Country and their connections and continuous care for the skies, lands and waterways throughout Australia.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999400186488583, \"rank\": 4.9023432101208765e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan thwarted Ariarne Titmus' bid to become the only swimmer in Olympic history to successfully defend Olympic titles in both the 200m and 400m freestyles.Source:AAP/Dean Lewins  Mollie O'Callaghan has pipped fellow Ariarne Titmus to win the gold medal in the women's 200m freestyle at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mollie O'Callaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mollie_O'Callaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Callaghan thwarted Titmus' bid to become the only swimmer in Olympic history to successfully defend Olympic titles in both the 200m and 400m freestyles.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old O'Callaghan clocked one minute 53.27 seconds in Monday night's final at the Paris La Defense Arena with Titmus (1:53.81) taking the silver medal.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory is O'Callaghan's first individual Olympic gold medal, adding to her three relay golds - two at the Tokyo Games three years ago and the 4x100m freestyle in Paris on Saturday night.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4580776070240065e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her triumph delivers Australia a fifth gold medal at the Paris Games, including three at the pool.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999400186488583, \"rank\": 4.9023432101208765e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, equestrian Chris Burton has unexpectedly added another silver medal to Australia's tally at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999954264467301, \"rank\": 4.571317215631459e-06, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\", \"score\": 0.7515418114886512, \"rank\": 0.2975206611571122, \"text\": \"Chris Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burton_(equestrian)\"}, {\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999400186488583, \"rank\": 4.9023432101208765e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burton has ridden to an individual eventing silver for Australia at Chateau de Versailles - on a loaned British horse he's only been riding for five months.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"score\": 0.7829657034272175, \"rank\": 0.2756136519805383, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999400186488583, \"rank\": 4.9023432101208765e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chateau de Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}, {\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7585881876852457, \"rank\": 0.3017024933588919, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 42-year-old Queenslander had ditched his show jumping speciality for another shot at eventing this year, and his switch paid off handsomely as he expressed his disbelief at steering new partner Shadow Man to second place.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.72085326904526e-14, \"text\": \"Queenslander\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1739, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.191673677818099e-16, \"text\": \"Shadow Man\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_No_1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Toowoomba's Burton, now based in the UK, was third overnight after the dressage and cross country but moved into the silver position after Monday morning's show jumping qualifying round when they had a clear round fractionally outside the time limit.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 2.096573431152069e-12, \"text\": \"Toowoomba\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"score\": 0.7829657034272175, \"rank\": 0.2756136519805383, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999955498424, \"rank\": 4.420599760357859e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then on a blazingly hot afternoon against the majestic backdrop of the Chateau, the fledgling combination cleared all 12 fences in the finale.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It put Burton in sight of Australia's first individual eventing triumph since Matt Ryan on Kibah Tic Toc in Barcelona 1992, as he knew 41-year-old German great Jung and his horse Chipmunk FRH were under the ultimate pressure.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\