ng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\"}, {\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chipmunk\", \"score\": 0.7364631096145272, \"rank\": 0.3578277086610968, \"text\": \"Chipmunk\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chipmunk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chipmunk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jung prevailed on 21.80 penalty points, 0.60 clear of Burton.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"score\": 0.999999832713925, \"rank\": 1.671026507198604e-07, \"text\": \"Jung\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Jung\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"score\": 0.7829657034272175, \"rank\": 0.2756136519805383, \"text\": \"Burton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Francis_Burton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Collett, who'd earlier led Britain to the team title, finished third on 23.10.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2453, \"end\": 2466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"score\": 0.9999948522782397, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Collett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\"}, {\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9402360314624626, \"rank\": 0.06356272301646848, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In women's basketball, the Opals had a disappointing performance in their starting game of the tournament, being outclassed by Nigeria 75-62.\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7758995175932354e-17, \"text\": \"Opals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian team were behind for most of the match, giving the ball away 26 times, and the Nigerian team took advantage.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2682, \"end\": 2696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5296836371524482e-14, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9997482709136575, \"rank\": 0.0002277589439326409, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999683713085443, \"rank\": 2.4565260604244964e-05, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an uncharacteristically poor game by the ranked number three in the world Opals, who only had 44.4 per cent from the free throw line, wasting the opportunity to lower the deficit of their defeat.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 3009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7758995175932354e-17, \"text\": \"Opals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alanna Smith provided the most points for Sandy Brondello's team, with 17, in a night that will need to be quickly forgotten by everyone in the Opals camp if they want to keep their hopes of advancing from this group alive.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3011, \"end\": 3023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alanna Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sandy Brondello\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\"}, {\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7758995175932354e-17, \"text\": \"Opals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's team will take up the charge on Tuesday, as they go up against Canada for their second game of the tournament, hoping to build up on their win over Spain on day one.\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3309, \"end\": 3315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9892434724762798, \"rank\": 0.008955357405797273, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3394, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999642064511608, \"rank\": 3.579163779160536e-05, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victorian boxer Harry Garside has been eliminated from the first round of the men's 63.5kg boxing tournament at the North Paris Arena by Hungarian Richard Kovacs.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3413, \"end\": 3422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6789874474759018, \"rank\": 0.46497256949015664, \"text\": \"Victorian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4580776070240065e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3550, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999124818728503, \"rank\": 7.01926267019213e-05, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the loss, the Tokyo bronze medallist said this was the nature of the sport and provided a harsh self-assessment.\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3601, \"end\": 3606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9890369206692926, \"rank\": 0.01108459720606917, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an athlete you put a lot of expectation on yourself and for the run to be over just like that, I feel like a failure right now,\\\" Garside said.\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really envisioned winning that gold medal for Australia, I really thought I could do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3898, \"end\": 3907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999400186488583, \"rank\": 4.9023432101208765e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hockeyroos made a dominant display as they annihilated Great Britain 4-0 in the second game of their tournament and will now play the USA on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3947, \"end\": 3957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hockeyroos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_fi